      "span_text": "RpoS is known to be upregulated in stationary phase through Hfq-mediated sRNA action.  To test the functionality of the tagged Hfq variants, we immuno-blotted extracts isolated from cells grown to either exponential or stationary phase and examined RpoS levels (Fig. 1C) ."
